    "Generative methods improved accuracy, precision, recall, F1 Score, and Specificity for RGB images and improvements in Structural Similarity Index (SSIM) and Peak Signal-to-Noise Ratio (PSNR) for satellite images.Li et al. [28] integrated GANs with a pyramid attention mechanism and transfer learning to improve segmentation accuracy for CT scans.",
    "For example, SimTrip [29] includes a self-supervised learning framework leveraging triplet manifestation to extract expressive features using extended views of data, effectively handling computational limitations and small batch sizes."
  ]
